description: SKF AB engages in the manufacture of machine and rotating equipment. The company is headquartered in Goeteborg, Vastra Gotalands and currently employs 41,151 full-time employees.  The firm's services include technical support, maintenance services, condition monitoring, asset efficiency optimization, engineering consultancy and training. The firm's segments include Industrial and Automotive. The firm develops and manufactures a range of products for the industrial market, including bearings, seals, lubrication systems and condition monitoring. The company also provides a range of services and solutions around the rotating shaft in the areas of machine health, reliability engineering and remanufacturing. The firm provides a range of products, solutions and services to manufacturers of cars, light and heavy trucks, trailers, buses and two-wheelers. The vehicle aftermarket is served directly, as well as indirectly through a network of distributors and dealers.
name: AB SKF
